title: #92Noon! Lavelle/Leber/Chavous/Sandelin
description: Lavelle in studio first hour because it's opening day for the Twins! Leber makes his normal Thursday appearance, elite draft opinions from Corey Chavous, then UMD hockey coach Scott Sandelin joins as his team begins the NCAA Tourney on Saturday!
